nodes.text: This unnamed Gand was a bounty hunter who tried to collect the bounty on Connor Freeman, a Human who owed a lot of credits to a powerful crime lord named Tayand. The bounty hunter tracked Freeman to a bar, who was sleeping on the bar's counter. Freeman, however, managed to evade capture; assisted by the bartender Quinny, who handed him a blaster, Freeman shot and killed the bounty hunter.
